:

1. *Brat* me je podsetio da odem na vreme. (My brother reminded me to go on time.)
2. Moj *brat* je isti kao i ja. (My brother is the same as me.)
3. Moj *brat* mi je pomogao da rešim problem. (My brother helped me to solve the problem.)
4. Moj *brat* je krao hranu iz frižidera. (My brother was stealing food from the fridge.)
5. Moj *brat* je preuzeo obavezu da prisustvuje događaju. (My brother took the responsibility to attend the event.)
6. Moj *brat* i ja smo igrali igrice cela večnost. (My brother and I were playing games for eternity.)